name: Kisaki | キサキ (Blue Archive)
description:
Kisaki | キサキ (Blue Archive)

I tried making a separate dataset so that her coat won't bleed with her normal outfit. I hope it actually makes a difference though. Samples tested at 1 strength on Anything v4.5.

Use these trigger words to get Kisaki's characteristics:

  • 1girl, kisaki, halo, hair bun, twintails, hair ornament

Normal Outfit:

  • china dress, sleeveless, coat, gloves

    • to remove her coat, simply add coat to the negative prompts.

Have fun!
